cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC. 

This paper is about developing a chatbot using deep reinforcement learning, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The evaluation of the system through A/B testing involves human-computer interaction, which could be categorized under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper discusses the potential of the system for real-world applications, which could be related to cs.SD (Software Engineering).
